instance-variables.LoadTxt: Your objective is to enter the laboratory, find the documents, and exit the laboratory.
Each door will lead you to another room full of things to discover.
Use W, A, S, D to move around. Left click to shoot your gun and R to reload weapon. E to interact with items.
You may want to save some supplies on your way back up.
Once you get the Documents and make it back here you will win.
Pick up this Card to access the Elevator.
